docs: add ARRAY_COLS and ARRAY_ROWS to variables.yaml

Used by the mock-array test to parameterize the N x N Element grid
(MACRO_PLACEMENT_TCL, macro check, power reports). Declaring them
in variables.yaml lets bazel-orfs build-time validation accept
them as known arguments instead of rejecting as unknown.

--- a/flow/scripts/variables.yaml
+++ b/flow/scripts/variables.yaml
@@ -1562,3 +1562,13 @@
     for generating Circuit Description Language output.
   stages:
     - final
+ARRAY_COLS:
+  description: >
+    Mock-array test: number of Element macro columns in the N x N grid.
+  stages:
+    - floorplan
+ARRAY_ROWS:
+  description: >
+    Mock-array test: number of Element macro rows in the N x N grid.
+  stages:
+    - floorplan
